events.name: Los Angeles Lakers at Milwaukee Bucks

headlines.description: — LeBron James scored a season-high 34 points in the opener of a seven-game road trip, helping the Los Angeles Lakers beat the Milwaukee Bucks 113-106 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: James, Lakers open long trip by beating Bucks 113-106

video.headline: LeBron leads Lakers past Bucks in battle of NBA heavyweights

highlights.headline: LeBron leads Lakers past Bucks in battle of NBA heavyweights
highlights.description: LeBron James puts up his first 30-point game of the season as the Lakers take down Giannis Antetokounmpo and the Bucks 113-106.

events.name: New Orleans Pelicans at Utah Jazz

headlines.description: — Donovan Mitchell scored a season-high 36 points, and the Utah Jazz rallied to beat the New Orleans Pelicans 129-118 on Thursday night for their seventh straight win.
headlines.shortLinkText: Mitchell helps Jazz beat Pelicans for 7th straight win

events.name: New York Knicks at Golden State Warriors

headlines.description: — RJ Barrett had a career-high 28 points and the New York Knicks matched their longest winning streak of the season at three games by beating the Golden State Warriors 119-104 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Barrett scores 28, Knicks beat Warriors for 3rd straight win
